re.alwyn974.openlauncherlib.minecraft

Class ForgeArgs

  • java.lang.Object
    • re.alwyn974.openlauncherlib.minecraft.ForgeArgs

  • public class ForgeArgs
extends java.lang.Object
    The Forge Arguments work only for Minecraft 1.13+ Version

    This class contains the specifics informations of the Forge Arguments
    The launchTarget, forgeVersion, minecraftVersion, forgeGroup and mcpVersion

    Since:
    3.0.5
